2/4/26 JR - Pellera indicated that customer renewed VMware contract for 1 year, and is looking to still engage Pellera on an alternative as their plan is to select a solution to replace VMware so that they do not have to renew next January. Working w/ Pellera on an update on next steps, and a face to face meeting w, the customer

