RE- 1/14/26 - Requalify oppty from Previous rep. Renewal is in 10/2026.

My root duty is managing installed SLES and SUMA instances, but I keep on track, how SUSE products grow and develops, to be prepared in future for hypothetical questions, where knowledge about available products on the market and their really functionality could be useful.

