<tr><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">Pellera</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">0</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">Grant MacEwan University (T)</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">KG Renewal Opportunity: 00143407 - 2026-04-01 - 2027-03-31 (52396.20CAD, origin 12M)</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">OP00489947</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">Kelley Gonsalves</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">Commit</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">Q2-2026</td><td align=right>3/31/2026</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">NAM NASA</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">USD</td><td align=right>38023.40</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">USD</td><td align=right>0.00</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">USD</td><td align=right>38023.40</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">3/3- KG - partner to quote customer</td><td>3/3 - KG - pricing sent to rachel.rajnovic@cdw.ca.  2 quotes presented, 1 year and 3 year with reduced qtys in year 2 and 3
