3/20 - JD: Spoke with Cameron about the Baffle application that is currently on AWS (RDS) which has been running since 2023. They didn&#39;t have the resources the last time they explored Rancher, but that they have hired Shreyans Bhardwaj it is now a possibility, but baby steps. They are first focusing on getting him up to speed with running, upgrading and maintaining the SLES environment, once he is comfortable and the time allows, they will begin the discussions around Rancher once again. Likely to begin in July or August. See notes from previous Rancher OPP: OP00398074 for more context from 2023.</td><td align=right>3/21/2025</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@"></td></tr>
