<tr><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">Computacenter</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">0</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">American Honda Motor Co., Inc. (T)</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">Honda NA ANDREW/Janet Renewal Opportunity: 00142362 - 2026-05-01 - 2027-04-30 (19038.00USD, origin 12M)</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">OP00487372</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">Andrew Carlsen</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">Commit</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">Q2-2026</td><td align=right>4/30/2026</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">NAM NASA</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">USD</td><td align=right>19038.00</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">USD</td><td align=right>0.00</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">USD</td><td align=right>19038.00</td><td style="vnd.ms-excel.numberformat:@">AC 3/5/26: Quote is with customer, and renewal is confirmed. Retrieving timeline to PO from customer this week.</td><td>JR 2/26/26 - S/w Core CC rep Andrew Anvari...speaking w/ him Monday about Industrial Edge/AI expansion opportunity. Andrew to continue working w/ Cindy at CC on renewal

